{"tid":862154,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無論件事發展成點，身為香港人既你一定要出黎","createTime":"2018-10-14T15:59:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-15T11:41:38.000Z","uid":7119,"like":175,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"9a412ab0f2f18a20e802be1f0044be2d607d6dac","tid":862154,"uid":7119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T15:59:02.000Z","msg":"過埋今個星期日、交左信之後<br />\n成個施政報告發表就已經過左差唔多一個禮拜<br />\n但係幾件事，包括東大嶼人工島、小麗DQ依然係未解決<br />\n香港人好快又會淡忘以上既事又返工返學<br />\n<br />\n雖然今次遊行/行動規模或者係未如理想，<br />\n但請你地每一位唔好放棄，我地依然有機會發聲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔該唔好怪學獨聯係美領冇任何行動，<br />\n請記住佢地目的係交請願信同美方展示友好<br />\n只要和平過左呢一步，有國際關注<br />\n以後做咩都會安全同埋有支持得多<br />\n<br />\n最後一句 要團結呀香港人"},{"pid":"8e80ffd24bfcf5e8111cc5194ae96a1c006bda53","tid":862154,"uid":7119,"like":56,"dislike":1,"score":55,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T16:01:38.000Z","msg":"我知道好多人都係未出黎但又想發聲<br />\n如果係因為身邊冇人出黎既話就請你做你圈子入面既第一個<br />\n出黎遊行示威發表意見係合法<br />\n<br />\n我相信經過雨革既香港人唔係咁政治冷感<br />\n如果有組織/人士肯領導的話 務必要支持"},{"pid":"4468af76bf5895adbb71261ccfa61f30959340b2","tid":862154,"uid":97451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T16:03:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f3a91edf8ea577c3657002122c99e1d7d21a4e09","tid":862154,"uid":77959,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T16:03:47.000Z","msg":"希望大家可以幫埋衝上大台，叫人去美領而比人打嘅巴絲<br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以幫下巴絲打 唔好再比左膠抹黑<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/862103/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/862103/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n<br />\n求下你哋share條片出去/直接佢屌鳩班左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82b06931e433ebad041cdaec8bae01d20d42bf70","tid":862154,"uid":7119,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T16:06:23.000Z","msg":"沉默係無用<br />\n你知我知單眼佬都知再咁落去香港真係會玩完<br />\n<br />\n我自問真係暫時無能力移民<br />\n請大家幫幫忙救下香港"},{"pid":"3d8c5cd1c95f1f4e4f448dcf34c37d637c02bd23","tid":862154,"uid":79709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T16:08:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e102de3ece92459483de6c193af1ce6e0fd0439","tid":862154,"uid":7119,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T16:08:57.000Z","msg":"我諗今次行動咁少人既原因或者係大家覺得抗爭冇可能<br />\n<br />\n但事實唔係 學獨聯今次真係好撚醒<br />\n捱到過聽朝就真係有好撚大機會可以傾數"},{"pid":"20033b31223d303b0e4edc26e7a648d1f62cc82b","tid":862154,"uid":7119,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T16:10:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e27f41209bc048ef7182a84c63f98f51f4b8a278","tid":862154,"uid":854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T16:10:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"14194070f1b80a17bbe824c388aca309702b9f39","tid":862154,"uid":43081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T16:11:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22f04bf3740335d3476dfb5d69f1325d8632bc14","tid":862154,"uid":175523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T16:11:30.000Z","msg":"推，要捱過今晚啊"},{"pid":"c94d36c6e4e0d8de553be736eb5adb17d9a2944c","tid":862154,"uid":7119,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T16:11:48.000Z","msg":"知大家要返工返學，<br />\n但請大家唔好頹 警犬宜家乜都唔敢做係有佢原因<br />\n證明學獨聯呢招有效 佢地唔會輕易拉人"},{"pid":"8378fb41bd1606bdca16e2af7662756e336d1019","tid":862154,"uid":112987,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T16:12:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7a448db3f09a32632f646a84a7483e4357fc13a6","tid":862154,"uid":7119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T16:13:31.000Z","msg":"媒體唔報導唯有靠大家瘋狂share<br />\n一傳十十傳百人人KOL 多view數過毒果啦"},{"pid":"12a6f4719c39ffd6ee396268b8748fa6bd62d3cf","tid":862154,"uid":19278,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T16:13:58.000Z","msg":"我開咗兩個白宮聯署, 關於香港問題<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/BwKQDU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/BwKQDU</a>"},{"pid":"26aaec18cf30d0f8293b409cb9d97d816c1c94d3","tid":862154,"uid":7119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12a6f4719c39ffd6ee396268b8748fa6bd62d3cf","tid":862154,"uid":19278,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T16:13:58.000Z","msg":"我開咗兩個白宮聯署, 關於香港問題<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/BwKQDU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/BwKQDU</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T16:14:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcd0d70a77ae212458974d5e65184f45acb581d7","tid":862154,"uid":7119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T16:16:07.000Z","msg":"仲有提提大家有ac既真係要多啲踢爆五毛fake news,<br />\n唔好比佢地打沉士氣 除左見一個block 一個之外一定要踢爆"},{"pid":"19813b2f4cbe1cc1b3fbc7ee142d4437c3120b25","tid":862154,"uid":7119,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T16:16:35.000Z","msg":"睇見隔離係咁話散水真係嬲，屌你老母圖都冇張係度fake人"},{"pid":"5d5c8f5898740d6c516ae9e0bdc98f8a5b216a3f","tid":862154,"uid":42449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T16:18:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7a4843ab6b79fa46cb387b4bbdfb417bfd028b7b","tid":862154,"uid":74848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T16:24:07.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ebcd6bb38fe9dbb18b0628a79a5ad8de040140f2","tid":862154,"uid":7119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T16:26:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hk